{{navbox
|name={{{name}}}
|state={{{state|autocollapse}}}
|image=[[Image:Apple-book.svg|30px|school image]]
|titlestyle=background-color:#CDDEFF;
|title={{{prefix|属于}}} {{{city|}}}{{{district|}}} {{{rootword|的学校}}}
|group1= {{#if:{{{secondary_schools|}}}|高中}}
|list1= {{{secondary_schools|}}}
|group2={{#if:{{{middle_schools|}}}|初中或高中}}
|list2={{{middle_schools|}}}
|group3= {{#if:{{{elementary_schools|}}}|小学}}
|list3= {{{elementary_schools|}}}
|group4={{#if:{{{private_schools|}}}|私校}}
|list4={{{private_schools|}}}
|group5={{#if:{{{other_schools|}}}|其他学校}}
|list5=  {{{other_schools|}}}
|group6= {{#if:{{{elemandmid_schools|}}}|一体制学校}}
|list6= {{{elemandmid_schools|}}}
}}<noinclude>This navigational template is for creating school navigation boxes for Canadian cities, regions or school districts.

Usage:
<pre>
{{Navbox 加拿大学校
|name={{subst:PAGENAME}} (required, used in creating the v/d/e links)
|city= (or district=)
|prefix= (alternative to "属于", optional)
|rootword=(alternative to "的学校", optional)
|secondary_schools= (optional)
|middle_schools= (optional)
|elementary_schools= (optional)
|private_schools= (optional)
|other_schools= (optional)
|elemandmid_schools= (optional)
}}<noinclude>
[[Category:Canadian education navigational boxes|{{PAGENAME}}]]
</noinclude></pre><noinclude>
